#~ msgid ""
#~ "Lumen is a plugin providing code-completion for the <ulink url=\"https://"
#~ "en.wikipedia.org/wiki/D_(programming_language)\"> D programming language</"
#~ "ulink>. It is just a connection between the editor and the D Completion "
#~ "Daemon (a server providing all the information) called DCD. The plugin "
#~ "currently supports all major features of the completion server: feeding "
#~ "the server with import files, displaying documentation and several types "
#~ "of completion:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Lumen — додаток, який реалізує автоматично доповнення коду для <ulink url="
